    • Constructor Detail

      • SceneStartScreen

        public SceneStartScreen()
        Main constructor for a SceneStartGame.

        Initialises a Scene textures for StartScreen. Including start menu for playing the game and options. When options are hovered over they will change texture indicating what the user is about to select.

      • update

        public int update()
        Update function for SceneStartScreen. Ends SceneStartScreen based on user input otherwise stays in scene.

        Returns an specified integer when you want to exit the screen else return scene_id if you want to stay in scene.

        Specified by:
        update in interface Scene
        Returns:
        returns an integer which is the scene_id of which screen is next (either this screen still or another)
